{"tid":1611034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔用豬咀，但我好想同大家講一樣野","createTime":"2019-10-02T00:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T02:11:06.000Z","uid":1968,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"48cfde85081a8b52ba1bce825a36b8c385f602ef","tid":1611034,"uid":1968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:35:39.000Z","msg":"好想講一樣野。<br />\n我一向唔用豬咀原因係方便撒退，<br />\n我覺呢樣野好緊要，<br />\n就算比狗逗都可以比較安全撒退。<br />\n<br />\n但我唔戴豬咀淨用普通口罩唔代表我唔可以上前線。<br />\n自認唔係最勇武個批，但都會上前線執下雞幫下手我絕對無問題，當我覺得唔舒服個陣自動會退後。<br />\n但每次上前線個陣都比叫我行後d, <br />\n仲深刻試過有次係金鐘前線退個陣，比中後排（同前線隔幾條街）一個戴曬豬咀嘅手足懶係野咁屌「tg呀，走啦，你食過未，係咪想食tg呀」,個刻得淡笑同無奈。"},{"pid":"cef1780297195639e372b2c07ac7684c002e7b55","tid":1611034,"uid":279689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:38:21.000Z","msg":"明白你感受，試過一次冇帶豬嘴就上前線比人扯返落去，唯有諗兄弟爬山，各自收行"},{"pid":"db9725c9e6552d8fdea566bc44254e83e28dd70e","tid":1611034,"uid":9,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:40:23.000Z","msg":"其實有時佢地都係唔想我地送頭姐<br />\n我多數企後返少少<br />\n救完一兩粒tg就多數自我收皮"},{"pid":"504f863c4264f08a9ee886994f1a09a71bb15df2","tid":1611034,"uid":160842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zT23cgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzT23cgM.jpg&h=5d058145&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FcYRk98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFcYRk98.jpg&h=23417bb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54d13a312366e3f956a02bdeaf0515af2b4b33c7","tid":1611034,"uid":47202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:44:47.000Z","msg":"用生命硬接tg, 口罩都冇個既街坊表示認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實tg又有咩好怕wor... 除非係企左入白煙裏面啦"},{"pid":"dd9e0a28435c222bae3a400b579f7f6c7bfd8d10","tid":1611034,"uid":263944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:48:17.000Z","msg":"612中信，粒